{"tid":2398904,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"塔門牛牛慘被虐 無打格影哂班罪人個靚樣","createTime":"2021-02-07T16:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T07:35:51.000Z","uid":98758,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"75f19460022f90c245727b8127dbea92175fa30e","tid":2398904,"uid":98758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:41:50.000Z","msg":"見到明周文化出左個post關於塔門牛牛被虐慘況<br />\n班人以為人類高高在上而對牛牛做出悲劣行為 至少要比佢地知道咁做唔係無後果<br />\n人類唔係大撚哂 咪撚再扮親親大自然<br />\n所以麻煩大家請廣傳佢地嘅惡行<br />\n同埋難得佢地個撚樣無打格 好想知佢地係咩人<br />\n//【#辛酸的塔門牛】牠的真情剖白：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3oOA0ad\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3oOA0ad&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=6d8dc799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3oOA0ad</a><br />\n不知從什麼時候開始，塔門人比牛多，一個個帳篷登上山坡，遺下一地斷掉的草根和膠袋。看到牛，有人拋擲石頭，有人硬拔牛角，有人一樽水照頭淋，每天左閃右避，成了牛牛日常。<br />\n但是，不願透露名字的塔門牛說：「人類是愛牛的，這些只是人類的小遊戲吧，我相信。」然而，牠的同伴都說受夠了，想移民，「但我哋真係好鍾意塔門！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/145499812_4143219135692898_2919676111639690093_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=oEzjN-dXs80AX8nxUdK&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=181e593dc7ab038ee425a884a5a8723a&amp;oe=604783CC\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F145499812_4143219135692898_2919676111639690093_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DoEzjN-dXs80AX8nxUdK%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26oh%3D181e593dc7ab038ee425a884a5a8723a%26oe%3D604783CC&h=344dc574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/145334455_4143211525693659_5264327042297413807_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=fq7KfaB1Pg0AX_z5TNo&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=e773f3fc723f3dabdfab54622b04c25a&amp;oe=60462032\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F145334455_4143211525693659_5264327042297413807_o.jpg%